,"msg":"減緊肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c80c4c6764d6bc35bc343ead459e1b210588eabc","tid":2274542,"uid":132749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a502bec3f0613cda69671d4b29abbdfe85d9809","tid":2274542,"uid":227988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T11:13:25.000Z","msg":"減緊肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T12:04:53.000Z","msg":"食一半舊，無咁易肥既"},{"pid":"8729126af240b6b5f246a6188d30a1ac4639a709","tid":2274542,"uid":132749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T14:01:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"db6d4667ed7239f1450d56ae18b0eea8576fb511","tid":2274542,"uid":230293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23c4916e52f634bc961d90149da5b2abac5a4f5d","tid":2274542,"uid":132749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T13:21:52.000Z","msg":"宜排成日見人講肉桂卷，不嬲好鍾意食宜隻野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />終於忍唔住手整左黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係好好食<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但宜個野真係好撚肥，勁多牛油同糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n次次整宜隻野都忍唔住係咁食，今個月我已經整左2次黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />第一次整完，又肚餓，諗住試一個先，製成品既片都未錄，抖下打下PS4，一邊拎黎食， 仆街，一邊打機一邊食，食食下先醒起未錄，得返2隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁唯有再整多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n焗既時候成屋牛油味，勁香，第二次一出爐錄完片又食左2個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食完真係要郁動多d先搞得掂。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n牛油🧈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vZ0J8U8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvZ0J8U8.png&h=3c5cec30&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j3C1a8y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj3C1a8y.png&h=7ab01e76&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c4D7Q8C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc4D7Q8C.png&h=4946092f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DN69j11.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDN69j11.png&h=2986ac81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fnDr6y6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfnDr6y6.jpg&h=3ad01c1f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ijcAfst.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FijcAfst.jpg&h=365e1453&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EP6htNw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEP6htNw.jpg&h=c74a9b52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n組織幾細緻，牛油既功勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dmS4Tee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdmS4Tee.jpg&h=6446f2ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/11/06/205354_a90d7369d72c1e9d80f4eb590503ddf1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F11%2F06%2F205354_a90d7369d72c1e9d80f4eb590503ddf1.jpeg&h=e0ea6087&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IcFX2gMQZ5g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIcFX2gMQZ5g&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9jC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=07cab205\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IcFX2gMQZ5g</a><br />\n<br />\n鍾意我條片既，<br />\n記得subscribe 我YouTube channel 呀！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtube.com/channel/UCGJHwItoXY4IkZX7efJvCXg\" d